1 cup water
1 cup ch. broth (no sodium)
1 tbspn vinegar
2 tbspn sugar
2 tbspn salt
Yukon gold potatos (peeled and cubed)

cook on med covered for 15 minutes. cook off some of the liquid on high, and reserve the liquid. 

1 tbsp white wine vinegar
1 tbsp veg oil
1 tbsp deijon

mash a few of the potatos in the dressing.

3/4 cup shallot minced
chives minced
corishon pickeled minced

toss in potatos. Serve at room temp.
